{
  "stem": "18281.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there sitting in the first row-- he was absolutely right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he's a half Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he survived in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His mother was a Catholic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was baptized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he passed for a, for a Mischling, for a mixed Catholic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You got me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I can find out for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we went swimming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went-- I had a bicycle and went to, to movies, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what little boys do, I guess-- nothing exciting, really.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, like I told you, I went to this little cheder.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And with a lot of, lot of help and pushing by my mother, I, I made my bar mitzvah in, in the synagogue that has been restored, the only synagogue in Vienna that was not demolished because it was inside an apartment building.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And while the Nazis trashed it and destroyed everything inside, they could not burn the building because Gentiles lived above it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Its the [INAUDIBLE] temple, which, which really translate as the little-- the side street temple.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I, I do recall that when we went back to the synagogue that had been restored recently, the Austrian government paid for that restoration.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It looked exactly the, the way I remember it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It has a blue ceiling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's kind of an oval synagogue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The whole shape of the, the room is oval.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the canopy has gold stars and has, has a blue ceiling on it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's a very old fashioned day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The women, for example, are not on the ground floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The women have to walk upstairs and kind of very narrow stairs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they have to sit upstairs, which is something my wife complained immediately.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess it was very simple.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
